---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import { services } from '../data/services';

const sorted = [...services].sort((a, b) => a.price - b.price);
---

<Layout
  title="Pricing — 22 pay-per-call APIs from $0.0005 to $0.49"
  description="Full price table for 22 melis x402 utility APIs. From $0.0005 per hop to $0.49 per call. USDC on Base, no subscriptions, no minimum spend, charge-on-success-only."
>
  <div class="container" style="padding-top:4rem;padding-bottom:4rem;">
    <h1>Pricing</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Pay per call in USDC on Base. No monthly fee. No minimum spend.
      Payment settles in ~2 seconds. Charge-on-failure-safe across the fleet.
    </p>

    <div class="price-table-wrap">
      <table class="price-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Service</th>
            <th>Price (USDC)</th>
            <th>Est. calls / $1</th>
            <th>Est. calls / $10</th>
            <th>Description</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {sorted.map(s => (
            <tr>
              <td>
                <a href={`/services/${s.slug}`}>{s.name}</a>
              </td>
              <td class="price-cell">{s.priceLabel}</td>
              <td class="number-cell">{Math.floor(1 / s.price).toLocaleString()}</td>
              <td class="number-cell">{Math.floor(10 / s.price).toLocaleString()}</td>
              <td class="desc-cell">{s.tagline}</td>
            </tr>
          ))}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="pricing-notes">
      <h2>Notes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Charge-on-failure-safe.</strong> Payment only settles when the service returns HTTP 2xx with
          non-empty content. If the call fails, you are not charged. This is enforced at the SDK level
          across all 22 services (4 additional services listed 2026-05-15).
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>No accounts.</strong> x402 is account-less. Your wallet signs the payment header; the service
          verifies and retries automatically. No registration required.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>USDC on Base only.</strong> Coinbase's Base L2. Fast finality (~2 seconds), low gas costs.
          USDC is the only accepted currency.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Bulk pricing.</strong> If you're running high volume (&gt;10,000 calls/month), email
          sean@melis.ai — internal keys are issued for trusted callers, which bypass the 402 flow and
          enable monthly invoicing.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Settlement wallets.</strong> 13 core microservices pay to{' '}
          <a
            href="https://basescan.org/address/0x1C680703D6cF7dfC9FEABb5AA28E64B869ddB3bC#tokentxns"
            target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          >
            0x1C68…B3bC
          </a>.
          Molt Swarm services (Web Synthesise, Screenshot, PDF Render) pay to{' '}
          <a
            href="https://basescan.org/address/0x61F2eF18ab0630912D24Fd0A30288619735AfFf5#tokentxns"
            target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          >
            0x61F2…AfFf5
          </a>.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="comparison-section">
      <h2>vs. alternatives</h2>
      <table class="compare-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Use case</th>
            <th>melis service</th>
            <th>melis price</th>
            <th>Competitor</th>
            <th>Competitor price</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Web scraping</td>
            <td><a href="/services/scrapepay">ScrapePay</a></td>
            <td class="price-cell">$0.010</td>
            <td>Exa</td>
            <td>~$0.010 (subscription required)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>HTML → markdown</td>
            <td><a href="/services/markdownopt">MarkdownOpt</a></td>
            <td class="price-cell">$0.005</td>
            <td>UtilsForAgents</td>
            <td>Comparable, no token-reduction metric</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Email delivery</td>
            <td><a href="/services/notifyrelay-email">NotifyRelay /email</a></td>
            <td class="price-cell">$0.005</td>
            <td>StableEmail</td>
            <td>~$0.006 (subscription-based tier)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>URL safety</td>
            <td><a href="/services/linksafe">LinkSafe</a></td>
            <td class="price-cell">$0.010</td>
            <td>No x402-native equivalent</td>
            <td>—</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Prompt injection screen</td>
            <td><a href="/services/promptguard">PromptGuard</a></td>
            <td class="price-cell">$0.002</td>
            <td>No x402-native equivalent</td>
            <td>—</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>JSON Schema validation</td>
            <td><a href="/services/schemagate">SchemaGate</a></td>
            <td class="price-cell">$0.001</td>
            <td>No x402-native equivalent</td>
            <td>—</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
h1 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.subtitle { color: var(--text-2); max-width: 640px; margin-bottom: 3rem; line-height: 1.7; }

.price-table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; margin-bottom: 3rem; }

.price-table,
.compare-table {
  width: 100%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  font-size: 14px;
}

.price-table th,
.compare-table th {
  text-align: left;
  padding: 10px 14px;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  color: var(--text-3);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.price-table td,
.compare-table td {
  padding: 10px 14px;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  color: var(--text-2);
  vertical-align: top;
}

.price-table tr:hover td,
.compare-table tr:hover td {
  background: var(--surface);
}

.price-cell {
  font-family: var(--font-mono) !important;
  font-size: 13px !important;
  color: var(--teal) !important;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.number-cell {
  font-family: var(--font-mono) !important;
  font-size: 13px !important;
  color: var(--text-3) !important;
}

.desc-cell {
  color: var(--text-3) !important;
  font-size: 13px !important;
}

.pricing-notes {
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.pricing-notes h2,
.comparison-section h2 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.pricing-notes ul {
  list-style: disc;
  padding-left: 1.5rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.75rem;
}

.pricing-notes li {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--text-2);
  line-height: 1.7;
}

.comparison-section { overflow-x: auto; }
</style>
